@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml

title 分布式锁核心组件关系图

left to right direction

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide empty members

package "API 层\n(distributed-lock-api)" as api_layer {

  interface DistributedLockClient {
    + tryLock(lockName, options)
    + execute(lockName, options, callback)
  }

  interface LockHandle {
    + unlock()
    + renew()
    + checkHeld()
    + assertHeld()
  }

  class LockOptions
  class LockResult
  class LockLease
}

package "Core 层\n(distributed-lock-core)" as core_layer {

  class DefaultDistributedLockClient
  class DefaultLockHandle

  class LockRuntimeState {
    - lost
    - released
  }

  interface LockWaiter
  class NoWaitLockWaiter
  class BackoffLockWaiter

  interface LockWatchdog
  class ScheduledLockWatchdog

  class OwnerTokenGenerator
  interface LockEventPublisher
  interface LockMetricsRecorder
}

package "Provider SPI 层" as spi_layer {
  interface LockProvider
  class LockProviderCapability
}

package "Provider 实现层" as impl_layer {
  class RedisLockProvider <<phase1>>
  interface FencingTokenProvider <<phase2>>
  class JdbcSequenceFencingTokenProvider <<phase2>>
  class ZkLockProvider <<phase3>>
  class EtcdLockProvider <<phase3>>
}

' 控制包的自然排列顺序
api_layer -[hidden]right-> core_layer
core_layer -[hidden]right-> spi_layer
spi_layer -[hidden]right-> impl_layer

' API 实现关系
DistributedLockClient <|.. DefaultDistributedLockClient
LockHandle <|.. DefaultLockHandle

' Core 内部扩展关系
LockWaiter <|.. NoWaitLockWaiter
LockWaiter <|.. BackoffLockWaiter
LockWatchdog <|.. ScheduledLockWatchdog

' Provider 扩展关系
LockProvider <|.. RedisLockProvider
FencingTokenProvider <|.. JdbcSequenceFencingTokenProvider
LockProvider <|.. ZkLockProvider
LockProvider <|.. EtcdLockProvider

' Client 主依赖
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockOptions
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockResult
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> OwnerTokenGenerator
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockWaiter
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockWatchdog
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockProvider

' Handle 主依赖
DefaultLockHandle --> LockLease
DefaultLockHandle --> LockRuntimeState
DefaultLockHandle --> LockProvider

' 事件和指标作为横切能力，用虚线表达
DefaultDistributedLockClient ..> LockEventPublisher
DefaultDistributedLockClient ..> LockMetricsRecorder
DefaultLockHandle ..> LockEventPublisher
DefaultLockHandle ..> LockMetricsRecorder

' Provider 能力
RedisLockProvider --> LockProviderCapability
DefaultDistributedLockClient ..> FencingTokenProvider : phase2 optional

legend right
  == 图说明 ==

  API 层：
  业务可见接口和结果模型。
  DistributedLockClient 是入口；
  LockHandle 是一次成功加锁后的租约句柄。

  Core 层：
  负责 tryLock / execute 编排，
  包括校验、加锁、等待、callback、
  watchdog、unlock、事件、指标和结果收敛。

  Provider SPI 层：
  定义底层锁实现的统一扩展点。

  Provider 实现层：
  RedisLockProvider 是一期实现。
  FencingTokenProvider 与 JDBC sequence 是二期实现。
  ZK / Etcd 是三期强协调扩展。

  Redis Provider 细节：
  见 L2-extension/redis-lock-extension-components.puml。
endlegend

@enduml